Interface ByteValue

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<ByteValue>, Mirror, PrimitiveValue, Value

    @Exported
public interface ByteValue
extends PrimitiveValue, Comparable<ByteValue>
    Provides access to a primitive byte value in the target VM.
